{"tid":2418999,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"狂射平民如戰場 反口襲散去群眾","createTime":"2021-02-23T04:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T06:19:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"87f7228303711e33800e3cc466204860d3e02623","tid":2418999,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210223/ZJRXTR7NF5ARXM25PZUD2SFN7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210223%2FZJRXTR7NF5ARXM25PZUD2SFN7U%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XqgSrXaipXgDiqSA7FZ3Rlo%3D&h=50ef0012\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210223%2FZJRXTR7NF5ARXM25PZUD2SFN7U%2F&h=dce2d2ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210223/ZJRXTR7NF5ARXM25PZUD2SFN7U/</a><br />\n<br />\n狂射平民如戰場 反口襲散去群眾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/opoF0v-6ntczUNi1cRC9biOrKOg=/1822x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D6U3AS6N7JGDFNWQ3U5FKQ2W4I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FopoF0v-6ntczUNi1cRC9biOrKOg%3D%2F1822x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD6U3AS6N7JGDFNWQ3U5FKQ2W4I.jpg&h=32778119&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■居泰緬人舉牌控訴軍方射殺16歲少年韋揚敦。路透社<br />\n<br />\n【 血腥鎮壓】<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：數十萬人上街 企業響應大罷工  民不懼死 緬甸掀22222革命<br />\n<br />\n緬甸曼德勒上周六的血腥鎮壓中有至少兩人死亡、14人受重傷。有目擊者憶述當日「猶如戰場」。當日有約20架車運載軍警到亞達納邦船塢鎮壓示威。軍警使用投射器、水炮、橡膠子彈甚至實彈作出攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屠殺羅興亞人步兵師涉事<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者指軍警當日「不停地」對手無寸鐵的示威者開槍，現場傳出尖叫聲，她與家人害怕得躲在家中，直至聽到有人高呼有人中槍才鼓起勇氣出外查看，發現「中槍的是我的兒子」。她42歲的兒子心口中槍後被送院救治。至今仍未知涉事軍警身份，已知的是2017年曾參與屠殺羅興亞穆斯林的第33輕步兵師有份參與鎮壓。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：央行高層地震 危及5,850億元經濟<br />\n<br />\n當日中槍死者分別是16歲少年韋揚敦（Wai Yan Tun）和36歲木匠德南溫（Thet Naing Win）。現場救護員指韋揚敦似乎被人以「非常強力的軍火」射擊致頭骨破裂，「他們開槍前毫無警告。」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n一名23歲示威者指當日軍警曾承諾如群眾解散就撤退，但反口攻擊正散去的群眾，並封路迫他們走進被發射催淚彈的區域。她指見到一名中年男子腹部和膝蓋中槍，「我可見到他的韌帶」。<br />\n<br />\n今日緬甸/英國《衞報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MHU9ZHVFsVUeWDo5yUhs2SE-9z8=/1330x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DO5E7A6URZAOJL2KDHCBP7Y2LY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMHU9ZHVFsVUeWDo5yUhs2SE-9z8%3D%2F1330x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDO5E7A6URZAOJL2KDHCBP7Y2LY.jpg&h=10a84ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■軍服縫上第33輕步兵師臂章（紅圈示）的士兵上周六出現在曼德勒街頭。法新社"},{"pid":"d962dad2ac46f008315571d2d20ac6be05cf692b","tid":2418999,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T04:34:57.000Z","msg":"黑警軍閥從來都係垃圾!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a55345c0a996e37749ce723390e057071e2ee0","tid":2418999,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}